## How to use this file

This file is loaded by Claude Code at the start of every session in this repo. It tells the agent what this project is, how to run common commands, and what safety rules to follow.

The rest of `.claude/` extends this:
- **Skills** (`.claude/skills/`) ‚Äî domain context loaded on demand
- **Commands** (`.claude/commands/`) ‚Äî slash commands for common workflows
- **Agents** (`.claude/agents/`) ‚Äî specialists Claude delegates to automatically
- **Rules** (`.claude/rules/`) ‚Äî language-specific conventions

Run `/help` for the full list.

